overview: Dishonorably discharged from the U.S. Marines after starting a barroom brawl that gets his leatherneck buddy "Tubby" Waters killed, hothead "Woody" Davis infiltrates a gang of Shanghai gunrunners to bring the culprit to justice.
tagline: THRILLS...WHEN THE DEVILDOGS SWING INTO ACTION!
title: The Leathernecks Have Landed
